data.description: **THOUSANDS BELOW CURRENT MARKET APPRAISAL!**Welcome home! This apartment unit in Points West is waiting for you! You'll find a lovely living room with a neutral palette, wood-look flooring, and balcony access. The dining room, with a charming light fixture, provides an ideal space for intimate dinners. The kitchen comes with solid surface counters, a tile backsplash, and built-in appliances. Can you believe the washer, dryer, & refrigerator all convey! The cozy bedroom features soft carpeting and a walk-in closet. Grab your favorite drink and relax on the balcony, a serene retreat for enjoying the outdoors. Situated near bus stops, restaurants, and shopping options. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
